*[[1911]] &amp;ndash; [[Jackie Ormes]], American cartoonist (d. 1985)
*[[1912]] &amp;ndash; [[Henry Jones (actor)|Henry Jones]], American actor (d. 1999)
*[[1914]] &amp;ndash; [[J. Lee Thompson]], British film director (d. 2002)
