* {{cite web | url=http://www.legislature.state.al.us/misc/history/constitutions/1861/1861.html | title=Constitution of the State of Alabama | year=1861 | publisher=[[Alabama Legislature]] | accessdate=July 3, 2008}}
* {{cite web | url=http://www.legislature.state.al.us/misc/history/constitutions/1819/1819.html | title=Constitution of the State of Alabama | year=1819 | publisher=[[Alabama Legislature]] | accessdate=July 3, 2008}}
